道記憶消失也值得<br />\n<br />\nOh... Your Love Forever<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">    閉上眼見到觀音<br />\n閉上眼兩腳一伸<br />\n醫護話收工失哂蹤～<br />\n怕快要見到高錕～ 描繪光纖細則～<br />\n難道記憶消失也值得 </span><br />\n<br />\nOh... Your Love Forever<br />\n閉上眼 看你消失 背向你 有我哭泣<br />\n倚傍着窗簾的瞬間<br />\n乍看世界已消失 描繪不出過失<br />\n沉在記憶中卻剩得我<br />\n閉上眼 看過天空 閉上眼 再次追蹤<br />\n追逐着身軀失了蹤<br />\n乍看世界已消失 重描繪當天氣質<br />\n沉重過哭泣也值得 憑着記憶跟你熱吻"},{"pid":"505d872c40c2c21ae3f51ff944b15cce86af994f","tid":1088260,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"曾做愛每次我也氣很喘～"},{"pid":"aebb71ea736490bb3a8b2d576ce1f64bd7fc0ada","tid":1088260,"uid":216662,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"505d872c40c2c21ae3f51ff944b15cce86af994f","tid":1088260,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"曾做愛每次我也氣很喘～"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:58:16.000Z","msg":"我用春袋溫暖 再暖 最後阿姐話我短<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d32e6235b2c9226cbc4893767cc5d157f09c6a9","tid":1088260,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aebb71ea736490bb3a8b2d576ce1f64bd7fc0ada","tid":1088260,"uid":216662,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"505d872c40c2c21ae3f51ff944b15cce86af994f","tid":1088260,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"曾做愛每次我也氣很喘～"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T04:58:16.000Z","msg":"我用春袋溫暖 再暖 最後阿姐話我短<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"亡命嘅季節 十四早報定到"},{"pid":"d63b8c0c1c10ec6fbf2f136e2f4212d98edff95d","tid":1088260,"uid":110018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T05:48:08.000Z","msg":"曾望見世界遍佈了醫院"},{"pid":"098ec0f9ff603e50b98ba582f0b081f88a646deb","tid":1088260,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d32e6235b2c9226cbc4893767cc5d157f09c6a9","tid":1088260,"uid":216662,"like